data.description: This wonderful ranch features all the right stuff! Generously sized 3 Bedrooms - 1.5 Baths - roomy living room with massive picture window! Full basement with additional sleeping area and half bath.  TONS of storage! There is solar powered supplemental heating system to keep those winter bills LOW! You will love the back yard with above ground pool and two sheds... a SHE SHED and a HE SHED... Close to schools and everything else you can think of too! Grab your favorite agent and schedule a tour. Don't miss this one!
